snippet.title: What makes a Good Robot?
snippet.description:
Good Robot on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/358...
For more info, please visit http://pyrodactyl.com/

Coming to Steam on April 5!

It's 2031. Humanity made robots to do all the boring jobs.
It left humans to do exciting things, like fighting all the malfunctioning robots.
But now that's your job. 
You're a Good Robot, and it's your mission to protect all the human beings on the colony.
There's got to be a few around somewhere...
